==安装

----从安装包：
1) 解压
2) 设置 HIVE_HOME
3) export PATH=PATH:$HIVE_HOME/bin

----从source：
1) 需要编译 

==设置

hadoop fs -mkdir /tmp
hadoop fs -chmod g+w /tmp
hadoop fs -ls /user/hive/warehouse            ---- (aka,also know as hive.metastore.warehouse.dir)
hadoop fs -chmod g+w /user/hive/warehouse


==Error Logs

/tmp/<user.name>/hive.log

